{"tid":2365644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國即日起禁止進口新疆所有棉花及蕃茄產品","createTime":"2021-01-14T02:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T05:05:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b619a7eb2be8d50c3386e00eb9836ad982c93d","tid":2365644,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"美國即日起禁止進口由新疆維吾爾自治區生產的棉花及蕃茄產品，因為有資料顯示，產品是由被拘留及強迫勞動的工人生產。海關及邊境保衛局發出暫停釋放命令，各口岸會扣起由新疆生產的服裝、紡織品、番茄罐頭及番茄醬等製品，局方強調不會容忍中國政府利用現代奴隸制，以低於公平市場的價格，向美國出口商品。國土安全部就要求中國立即關閉再教育營，停止侵犯人權。 特朗普政府過去亦實施過針對新疆經濟制裁，上月初已禁止從新疆生產建設兵團進口棉花及相關產品。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2374725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2374725&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=7967bb1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2374725</a>"},{"pid":"13534332d25252489ae602ebff819fd30ad8230c","tid":2365644,"uid":256837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"好快又賣得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5927223fb97e40e1051b9f549710e6688505d87","tid":2365644,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0053a325a1cc7cb083de6d39a0be47c55234e70c","tid":2365644,"uid":100347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"禁啦<br />\n無印良品 Unique 都唔幫襯"},{"pid":"ff8b1f0abd4f6345d948b3e1c6cd777efeec624a","tid":2365644,"uid":245484,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"20 號就賣得返啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能仲會因為禁左一個禮拜而賠錢添 <im